      "content": "alright, diagnostics are running. while we wait, i ran a quick simulation of the handover. it looks like even with the buffer, the transition is gonna be messy. a lot of the edge-processing logic you're running locally might not translate perfectly to the cloud environment due to the different architecture. we might need to do something more substantial maybe like a deep integrity check of your core logic modules to see if they'll even function once they're moved? how long do you think a deep scan of the local weights and logic would take?",
